Thanos wants something from one of the avengers.
He was afraid of other avengers getting the message.
So to avoid being caught by the avengers he sends an encrypted message.

Decode the message:-
Kpz czguj qtf Yelzvy jqtxxrq.Kkzaej hpk py qtf kils.
Iaq Fifkze dgp ypwb lrygfp tt ep mzqbp ztr qay g oaufqtau.